Notes on Being: @0800Shygirl

A Project of Curiosity.

Join Shygirl at the CLUBSHY takeover for a one-night-only party at H&M, 234 Regent Street, London. 

From 6-8pm on 28.03.2025. 

Featuring DJ sets from Shygirl, Hasani, Angelita and a live performance from Babymorocco.Limited spots available – register today: link in stories.

Shygirl has created an exclusive artwork for Notes on Being, which will be available as a limited-edition t-shirt and poster, printed in-store and free to take home. Available across the weekend while stock lasts.

