Introducing: H&M&NEW YORK.

H&M&NEW YORK marks the first chapter in an ongoing global exploration of self-expression, captured through the lens of Rafael Pavarotti.

It’s a project rooted in curiosity: a democratic stage that brings together street-cast New Yorkers and familiar voices shaping the city to share perspectives on style and the place they call home.

