Art In Progress | A tribute to contemporary art, a celebration of creative expression.​ A collaboration with @ad_spain. 

We are proud to be part of ARCOmadrid, supporting the artistic dialogue that shapes our times. In partnership with the renowned studio Carbajo Hermanos @carbajohermanos, Art In Progress brings together the works of Lucía Bayón, Lara Fluxà, and Kiko Pérez—artists exhibiting at ARCO—to explore the intersection of fashion and contemporary art. Stay tuned as we unveil this artistic dialogue throughout the weekend.

Artists & Art Galleries: 
@luciabayon, @galeriabelmonte
@larafluxa, @bombonprojects
@psikokiko, @ehrhardtflorezgallery

