LIMITED EDITION SS25 | A vision brought to life.

Our latest show unveiled a living gallery through the Art In Progress initiative, where fashion seamlessly blends with art. Each piece stands as a tribute to the creative journey, blurring the boundaries between design, fashion, and artistic expression.

@Laurentmartinlobamboo: Cosmic Brother, 2014-2016.
Weather beaten bamboo, steel rings and hooks, ceramic balls.

@Ombredansleau: Bailaora.
Stoneware clay with grog fired at high temperature.

@esthergaton_: Un martillo vienne hacia ti E, 2021
Linen fabrics died with turmeric, beetroot and iron solution, steel bars, brackets, oil pastel and watercolour. 

@Antoniogonzalez.me: Work2.
Oil on Canvas.

@Ombredansleau: Feminae, Morbid num II.
Stoneware clay with grog fired at high temperature.

@tamararroyo: Ruina Contemporánea. Serie Un Fatal descontento de lugar. 2021. 
Concrete and ceramic. 

@emeca___: Untitled, 2024. 
Acrylic on Canvas.

@pamenpereira: Los huesos de la tierra. 
A cascade of polystyrene stones coated in cement.

@Armandomesias: Ostinato, 2023.
Oil, spray paint, charcoal, pen, Totomoxtle ash, pigment, and acrylic on patchwork of cotton and denim.

Galleries:
 
@Vasto_gallery
@Alzueta_gallery
@nfnievesfernandez 
 
